Cloudflare Zero Trust VPN plugin for OPNsense.

Integrates Cloudflare Zero Trust networking as a first-class VPN component,
supporting WARP (MASQUE/HTTP3 and WireGuard modes) and Cloudflare Tunnel.

Features:
- WARP via MASQUE/QUIC (Connect-IP protocol, RFC 9484)
- WARP via WireGuard (kernel WireGuard)
- Cloudflare Tunnel (cloudflared)
- Multiple organizations and tunnels
- Split and full tunnel modes
- Automatic key rotation
- Health monitoring and diagnostics
- Native OPNsense GUI integration

Bundled binaries (FreeBSD amd64, no external downloads required at install):
- cfzt-warp: MASQUE/WireGuard tunnel daemon (built from source)
- cloudflared: Cloudflare Tunnel connector (official Cloudflare release,
  version pinned in Makefile CLOUDFLARED_VERSION)

WWW: https://www.cloudflare.com/zero-trust/
